						               													<description>You're on the hunt for One-Eyed Willy's fabled treasure with the Fratellis close behind in this immersive cooperative family strategy game! Maneuver your way through the tunnels and around challenges like the Bone Piano to discover the &amp;quot;Rich Stuff&amp;quot; at the end of the journey but only if you can stay ahead of the Fratellis! Bring back your best childhood memories and watch your kids fall in love with this classic adventure movie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Goonies Game is here to bring you into the thrilling world of the Fratellis, the Bone Piano, the Goon Docks, and more. Work together to discover the rich stuff at the end of the journey! One-Eyed Willy has his hands on the treasure you are searching for. Solve the challenges with the silver doubloon and the copper bones key to unlock the secrets and find the treasure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, you work together with the other players to run away from the Fratellis and clear challenges (dice rolls and blind guessing) before they reach you. All 4 groups of Goonies are always in play so these will need to be divided over the number of players. Players play cards on their turn to move (mandatory) and can optionally try challenges (if they're on a challenge space), try to break free from the clutches of the Fratellis (die roll) and play a quote (a one time effect played, unique per card).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Goonies need to reach the end of the board to win the game, they will also need to have at least 25 'rich stuff' which are found at the end of the board and mostly comes down to blindly taking the correct ones.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
